    },
    {
      "id": "5acafaa7aff09e00007432c0",
      "text": " 公理的設計―複雑なシステムの単純化設計",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523251879,
      "updated": 1523251942
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafaf1aff09e00007432c4",
      "text": "  [NamPyo Suh] (著), 中尾 政之 (翻訳), 飯野 謙次 (翻訳), [畑村 洋太郎] (翻訳)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523251953,
      "updated": 1523251976
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafac3aff09e00007432c3",
      "text": " [Amazon https://amzn.to/2EwFU8G]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523251908,
      "updated": 1523251908
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafb53aff09e00007432c5",
      "text": " 原著 [Axiomatic Design Theory for Systems | SpringerLink https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s001639870001]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252052,
      "updated": 1523252080
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafb53aff09e00007432c6",
