      "updated": 1523252059
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafbefaff09e00007432c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252207,
      "updated": 1523252207
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafbefaff09e00007432ca",
      "text": "\t1.6 公理的アプローチとアルゴリズム的アプローチ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252207,
      "updated": 1523252221
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafbfdaff09e00007432cb",
      "text": " CA: 顧客属性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252221,
      "updated": 1523252288
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafc40aff09e00007432cc",
      "text": " FR: 要求機能",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252288,
      "updated": 1523252308
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafc59aff09e00007432ce",
      "text": " C: 制約条件",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252313,
      "updated": 1523252316
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafc4eaff09e00007432cd",
      "text": " DP: 実体領域の設計解",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252303,
      "updated": 1523252334
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafc93aff09e00007432cf",
      "text": " PV: プロセス変数(プロセス領域の生産条件)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252372,
      "updated": 1523252386
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafcbfaff09e00007432d1",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/407262cb7c8e2caaa4d54e0a27e79399]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252416,
      "updated": 1523252416
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafcbdaff09e00007432d0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252414,
      "updated": 1523252414
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafd44aff09e00007432d2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252548,
      "updated": 1523252548
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafd44aff09e00007432d4",
      "text": "\t独立公理 (Independence Axlom)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252549,
      "updated": 1523252572
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafd5caff09e00007432df",
      "text": " \tFRは設計目標を記述する最小個数の独立した必要条件として定義され、FRの独立性は常に保たれねばならない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252572,
      "updated": 1523252641
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafd5caff09e00007432e0",
      "text": " 情報公理 (Information Axlom)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252573,
      "updated": 1523253202
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafda9aff09e00007432e1",
      "text": " \t独立公理を満たす設計の中で最小の必要情報量を持つものを最良の設計とする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252649,
      "updated": 1523252670
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafdc7aff09e00007432e4",
      "text": "\t\tつまり、成功確率が最も高い設計が最も良い設計である(?)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252679,
      "updated": 1523253231
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb01bfaff09e00007432e8",
      "text": "  情報の定義:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523253696,
      "updated": 1523253701
    },
    {
      "id": "5acb01b0aff09e00007432e6",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/40483c4192e30285a36606a3be0e8e2e]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523253681,
      "updated": 1523253701
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafdc6aff09e00007432e3",
      "text": "   つまり彼が言う「情報」とは成功確率が1の時0になり、0の時に∞になる値である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252678,
      "updated": 1523253766
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafda9aff09e00007432e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252649,
      "updated": 1523252678
    },
    {
      "id": "59dcdb2caff09e0000e3c7a0",
      "text": " 要求機能から設計への対応付けを行列Aで表現する。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507646252,
      "updated": 1523252091
    },
    {
      "id": "5acaffaeaff09e00007432e5",
      "text": " \tFR = A DP",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523253167,
      "updated": 1523253177
    },
    {
      "id": "59dcdb7faff09e0000e3c7a3",
      "text": "  行列が対角行列の時、独立設計、三角行列のとき準独立設計, それ以外のときには干渉設計。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507646335,
      "updated": 1523253165
    },
    {
      "id": "59dcdbc1aff09e0000e3c7a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507646401,
      "updated": 1507646434
    },
    {
      "id": "59dcdbc6aff09e0000e3c7a5",
      "text": " 公理1 (独立公理): 設計行列は独立設計か準独立設計でなければならない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507646406,
      "updated": 1523252094
    },
    {
      "id": "5acafb7eaff09e00007432c8",
      "text": " 公理2 (情報公理): 独立公理を満たす設計の中で情報量の最も少ないものが最適な設計である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523252095,
      "updated": 1523252095
    },
    {
      "id": "59dcdbe3aff09e0000e3c7a8",
